    "causal_summary": "The `@multi-ai-council` agent today returns deliberation results inline to chat with no packet-level persistence, breaking parity with `@deep-research` (writes to `research/`) and `@deep-review` (writes to `review/`). This packet introduces the `ai-council/` subfolder convention so council outputs become first-class, audit-friendly packet artifacts that support iteration and resume. The convention stays lightweight: no skill folder, no slash command, no YAML workflow — just an agent body update plus 4 shared reference files.",
